This is a great local coffee shop with awesome crepes! My wife and I rode our bikes over for brunch. We both enjoyed the chipotle crepe. I had an Americano and she had a blended white chocolate. Both were very good. It's a great addition to the neighborhood, and we will certainly be coming back! Would love to see some bike racks in front though.

